   cd mitm-man-in-the-middle-
Install Dependencies:
Ensure you have Python 3 installed. Then, install the required Python packages:

bash
Kopyala
D√ºzenle
pip install scapy manuf
üöÄ Usage
Run the script with the appropriate options:

bash
Kopyala
D√ºzenle
python mitm.py -g <gateway_ip> -t <target_ip>
Options:

-g, --gateway: IP address of the network gateway.

-t, --target: IP address of the target device.

Example:

bash
Kopyala
D√ºzenle
python mitm.py -g 192.168.1.1 -t 192.168.1.100
This command initiates an ARP poisoning attack between the specified gateway and target.

